  "text": "Continuous variables were summarized as median and interquartile ranges (IQR) and compared using Wilcoxon rank sum test. Categorical variables were reported as counts and percentages and compared with Chi square test or Fisher's exact test as appropriate. Further details on the statistical analyses on the SHADE cohort have been published previously [CITATION_1] .",
